#----------------------------------------------------
# a) ABS correction
#----------------------------------------------------
# VHeight                    2    
# VRadius                    0.4  
# VAttenuationXSection       5.1  
# VScatteringXSection        5.08 
# VanaNumberDensity          0.072
# VNumberOfSlices            10   
# VNumberOfAnnuli            10   
# VNumberOfWavelengthPoints  100  
# VExpMethod                 Normal
#----------------------------------------------------
